data.description: Location, location, location! Well cared for home on Terre Haute's popular east side sitting in Birch Grove sub-division. Home offers many amenities including three bedrooms, two and a half baths, eat-in kitchen with stainless appliances and a formal dining area. Living room is open, spacious and perfect for entertaining with the fireplace equipped with a gas log. Master bedroom has a private bath and walk-in closet. You'll enjoy the upstairs laundry which is convenient and located off the Bonus room! Newly finished basement offers a large living area with more space for exercise equipment, game table and so much more. Hurry on over before this one is sold. We'd love to show you today - call Chip 812.249.3114 or Lynda 812.201.3034 Convenient to Deming and Dobbs Park, Heritage Trail, Meijer, Walmart, a new Starbucks and I70.
data.whatILove: Beautiful finished open space (approximately 90% finished) in the basement! Perfect for TV, video games, exercise and so much more.  Location is in the heart of Terre Haute being so close to city parks - Deming and Dobbs, a short walk or bike ride to the Heritage Trail too.  Easy drive from Hulman to US 46 to shop at Meijer, Walmart, and the new Aldi!  New Starbucks will be in front of Meijer soon.  Eateries are also along this corridor with access to I70.
